data.description: Nestled perfectly in the Chatsworth Mountains, this property holds profound historical significance. Offering unparalleled 270-degree views of both the majestic mountains and the bustling cityscape, opportunities like this emerge scarcely. The circular 2400 sq ft residence, featuring 4 bedrooms and 2 baths, underwent a comprehensive renovation in 2023. Every facet was meticulously updated, encompassing new stucco, windows, roof, central air, kitchen, bathrooms, flooring, electrical, and plumbing.  Moreover, the home offers the potential to be divided into two distinct units, each boasting its own full kitchen, bathrooms, alongside spacious sitting and dining areas. Encompassing over 7000 sq ft, this residence is an ideal space for both entertainment and seclusion. Standing proudly among three other homes on the same street, it enjoys exclusive access via its private driveway, offering a haven of privacy.  While lacking a garage, the property easily accommodates over 10 cars through street parking and designated areas. The community itself is renowned for its exclusivity, privacy, and enveloping rustic landscape. Situated nearby are over 1.7 million dollars' worth of new homes, with convenient proximity to the freeway, bustling city shopping districts, and entertainment hubs. Notably, the property is adjacent to a prestigious, award-winning private school catering to students from kindergarten to 12th grade.  This unique property presents an exceptional opportunity to own a complete compound, suitable for diverse purposes such as multi-generational living, a serene private retreat, or potential subdivision. Its profound significance and impeccable nature make it a rare gem in the market. The longer one spends within its confines, the more its exceptional qualities reveal themselves, creating an environment of unmatched allure and charm.
